quran[7]{c,v,t}:
  59,10,"Wid id iusan deffir sen, qqaĂŽen: ""a Mass nne$! SemmeĂȘ a$, akked wamaten nne$, i $ d izwaren ar liman. Ur Ppara deg ulawen nne$, a$ullu n wid iumnen. A Mass nne$! KeĂ§Ă§, s tidep, d UmĂąin IpĂȘunun""."
  59,11,"Ur twalav ara ixabiten, la qqaĂŽen i watmaten nnsen ijehlen, seg wAt Tezmamt: ""ma ssuff$en kwen, ard a neffe$ yidwen, ur nessemĂȘas i yiwen, d awez$i, mgal nnwen. Ma nnu$en kwen, ar ad awen nefk afus"". Ad Icehhed Ăebbi, ar nitni d ikeddaben."
  59,12,"Ma ssuff$en ten, ur teff$en yidsen. Ma nnu$en ten, ur asen ppaken afus. Ma Ăąawnen ten, ad rewlen; ihi, ur ppĂąawanen!"
  59,13,"D kunwi, sennig Ăebbi, ay ugaden idmaren nnsen, ayagi, acku nitni d agdud ur nefhim."
  59,14,"Ur kwen pna$en, ddukwlen, siwa ma di temdinin ippwaĂ©eĂŽben, ne$ deffir leswaĂŽ. Lbe$wv garasen qesseĂȘ. A pxilev dduklen, wanag rwin wulawen nnsen. Ayagi, acku nitni d agdud ur nepxemmim."
  59,15,"Cban wid i ten id izwaren s cwiĂź kan, jeĂŽĂŽben lwexda igiten nnsen, fellasen aĂąaqeb aqeĂŽĂȘan."
  59,16,"Cban CciĂźan, mi s inna i umdan: ""ejhel""! Mi ijhel, inna: ""nek mgirrde$ k, nek ugade$ Ăebbi, Mass imavalen""!"
